<H2> Wednesday 21 April 1993 </H2>
    <H3>Forum on Risks to the Public in Computers and Related Systems</H3>
    <I><A HREF="http://www.acm.org">ACM</A>
Committee on Computers and Public Policy, Peter G. Neumann, moderator</I><P><B>
