<LI><A HREF="/Risks/17.04.html#subj3">Make a Call, Turn Off the Power (Mike Winkelman)</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="/Risks/17.04.html#subj4">Boeing 777 has dainty feet (Nathan Myers)</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="/Risks/17.04.html#subj5">Risks of HCI designed by non-typist (Pete Mellor)</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="/Risks/17.04.html#subj6">Endless loops in Voice Mail (Dick Mills)</A></LI>
<LI><A HREF="/Risks/17.04.html#subj7">Computer will control Nick Ingram's execution (Mike Wilson)</A></LI>
